| **Test Factories** | `makeTestDb()` (in-memory), `makeTestApp()` (full app), `makeTestDir()` (tmpdir) |

All test code follows the helpers pattern with no file I/O or external resources—tests run in isolation, in parallel, with automatic cleanup.

